## timedResult variable

Similar to `timed()`<!-- -->, but produces no output and instead returns tuple of `fn`<!-- -->'s result and the time measurement.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
timedResult: <T>(fn: () => T) => [T, number]
```
